metadata.name: Pillar of Yorick
metadata.description: A tribute to the magnificent, all-seeing ape. This trophy rewards your vision and commitment throughout the first ever BlackPool Cup. Let the faint radiation from this Chimpanzanite creation illuminate your home and forever alter your genetic makeup from its position atop your mantlepiece. You won. You will forever be the champion of the first ever BlackPool Cup. Not even Kong himself can take that away from you.
